          "value": {
            "data": {
              "markdown": "```\n#!/usr/bin/env bash\nset -euo pipefail\n\nif npm run test --silent; then\n  exit 0\nelse\n  echo \"Tests are failing. Fix all test failures before creating a PR.\" >&2\n  exit 2\nfi\n\n```"
            },
            "mutability": "Mutable",
            "type": "MARKDOWN"
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "8",
          "value": {
            "data": {
              "markdown": "```json\n{\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"PreToolUse\": [\n      {\n        \"matcher\": \"Bash\",\n        \"hooks\": [\n          {\n            \"type\": \"command\",\n            \"command\": \".claude/hooks/block-dangerous.sh\"\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\n```"
            },
            "mutability": "Mutable",
            "type": "MARKDOWN"
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "19",
          "value": {
